	the case may be), the performance by the Company and the Manager of its obligations hereunder and to the following additional conditions precedent:




	(a) The Company and the Manager shall furnish to the Representative at the time of purchase and at each additional time of
	purchase, as the case may be, an opinion of Hunton & Williams LLP, special counsel for the Company and the Manager, addressed to the Underwriters, and dated the time of purchase or each additional time of purchase, as the case may be, with
