Pingora Asset Management   –  Fund Management
































































Fund Management
 HomeFund Management 



 





Pingora MSR Opportunity Fund

Pingora Asset Management LLC, launched its’ first fund in 2013. The Fund seeks to maximize risk-adjusted returns by investing in securities intended to provide certain economic benefits arising from one or more specified pools of mortgage servicing rights. An MSR is a contractually created right to service a mortgage loan or pool of mortgage loans over the life of such loans in exchange for a specified fee stream, subject to continued performance of services in accordance with the servicing contracts. 
 





Comments are closed.












Pingora MSR JV I-A, LP  Financing | Newest SEC Filings

















Newest Filings











Pingora MSR JV I-A, LP  Financing
Pingora MSR JV I-A, LP just submitted form D announcing  Indefinite equity financing.  This is a new filing. Pingora MSR JV I-A, LP was able to sell $550,000,000. The total private offering amount was Indefinite. The financing was made by 3 investors. Minimal accepted investment was $50,000,000. The financing document was filed on 2016-12-02. Pingora MSR JV I-A, LP is based in  1755 BLAKE STREET SUITE 200 DENVER 80202. The firm's business is Pooled Investment Fund. The form was signed by  Michael Lau.





